# Runner shell configuration

## Default pane prompt is stable

The default pane prompt should be stable across test environments.

    :bins env

> [!NOTE]
> 'env' is available.

    :tmux respawn-pane -k -t 0.0 'env ENV=$HOME/.shrc PS1="sh$ " /bin/sh -i' (success)

    :tmux resize-window -x 80 -y 2 -t 0 (success)

    :snap

```terminal
sh$

```

## New windows also have stable prompt

Creating a new window without a command should still produce the same stable prompt.

    :tmux new-window -d -n fresh 'env ENV=$HOME/.shrc PS1="sh$ " /bin/sh -i' (success)
    :pane fresh.0
    :tmux resize-window -x 80 -y 2 -t fresh (success)

    :snap

```terminal
sh$

```

